item.title: The homeomorphisms of the Sierpi\'nski carpet are not classifiable by countable structures
item.description: arXiv:2404.01472v1 Announce Type: new Abstract: We show that the homeomorphisms of the Sierpi\'nski carpet are not classifiable, up to conjugacy, using isomorphism types of countable structures as invariants.
item.dc:creator: Dhruv Kulshreshtha, Aristotelis Panagiotopoulos
